<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: TimesN; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 237); text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">晚霞里暖融融的猫咪&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">午后长长的斜阳&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">疏林里绰约的动影&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">晚归时昏黄的灯光&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">红墙细雨，明窗暗影&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">斜晖脉脉，影悠悠</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJu2SI5RI9Ed3n2P89d6WcQt4UZgZAKU0G90Snhdt9WjTNlAk4f5JE8TmSC02oC4CiaqVZ6oX5Qeug/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="251" height="231" style="width: 251px; height: 231px;"/></p>